data.title: Find UK Scanner Frequencies, Radio Reference UK
data.meta_description: Find and Map Frequencies in the UK to listen to on your radio scanner, our unique range feature allows to find signals within a user defined distance from your Town or Postcode.
data.text:
Use any web browser to search the WTR and find local frequencies to program into your scanner. Works on any PC or Mobile running Windows, Mac, IOS, Android and more.

The most comprehensive and up to date UK radio scanner frequency database covering WTR, PMR, Airband, Airports, Air Control, Mil Airband / Airfields, Ham and more.
